[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0m"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[1;34mThe name of the second largest city in Turkey is \"Diyarbakır\", which contains both the dotted and dotless letters i.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0m"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;34m*/\r\n"]
