[0.001, "o", "\u001b[1;34mMethod .Unicode~utf8proc_transform\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0m"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;34mThe purpose of this method is to support all the transformations provided by utf8proc.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0m"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;34mTakes a byte string as input (UTF-8 encoded), returns a new transformed byte string as output (UTF-8).\r\n"]
